## Description {#details}

Implementation of directive handling which is shared across all Darwin targets.

Definition at line 42 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/mc/lib/mc/mcparser/darwinasmparser-cpp">DarwinAsmParser.cpp</a>.
